         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-d79665"><!-- p4l3-r10 -->
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d79665-Hd1e108">Rubrica 10</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d79665-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De famulis et domesticis</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d79665-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>
      ¶ De famulis et domesticis. Rubrica. 10
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d79665-d1e119">
               <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>SAlomon in prouerbiis. c.
      <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>15 <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d79665-Qd1e125">Conturbat
        <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>Rdomum suam qui sectatur auaritiam. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d79665-d1e131">
               <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d79665-Qd1e135">¶ Isocrates in exhortationibus. c.
        <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>2. Esto adherentibus tractabilis non subli
        <lb ed="#V" n="17" break="no"/>mis: nam despicientium tumorem vix equi
        <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>dem tolerabunt serui: modum vero tractabi
        <lb ed="#V" n="19" break="no"/>lium cuncti ferunt alacriter. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d79665-d1e148">
               <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d79665-Qd1e152">¶ Iesus filius sirach in ecclesiast. c. 8. Noli
        <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>esse sicut leo in domo tua euntes domesticos
        <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>tuos et opprime subiectos tibi. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d79665-d1e160">
               <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d79665-Qd1e164">¶ Seneca epistolarum ad lucillum: li. 18. e.
        <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>5. Timeri tam domi quam foris molestum est:
        <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>tam a seruis quam a liberis. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d79665-d1e172"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d79665-Qd1e174"> Idem de breuita
        <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>te vite: Eorum minserrima est conditio: qui
        <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>nec suis quidem laborant occupationibus: ad
        <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>alienum dormiunt sonum ad alieuum am
        <lb ed="#V" n="29" break="no"/>bulant gradum: ad alienum comedunt appetitum. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d79665-d1e186">
               <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d79665-Qd1e190">¶ Boetius de consolatione: lib. 3 c. 9. Que
        <lb ed="#V" n="31"/>pestis est efficacior ad nocendum quam fami
        <lb ed="#V" n="32" break="no"/>liaris inimicus. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d79665-d1e198">
               <lb ed="#V" n="33"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d79665-Qd1e202">¶ Bertrandus vconomica. c. 15. Famulum
        <lb ed="#V" n="34"/>alti cordis repelle: vt futurum inimicum.
        <lb ed="#V" n="35"/>Famulum tuis moribus blandientem re
        <lb ed="#V" n="36" break="no"/>pelle. Famulum de facili se verecundantem
        <lb ed="#V" n="37"/>dilige vt filium. </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
